egister to the sites is to \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"b8 c-r-m-r-t-l\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"t\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"m clear\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/static/a/500012720/a1011681_3.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWriting letters unites hearts. \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWriting letters is the most popular way of knowing Russian women on our site. Especially important is writing first letter as it gives to a woman the first general idea about you. That\u2019s why the letter should contain some basic information about yourself, give to the woman some facts about you, but do not give her any details \u2013 let she ask for the details by herself.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"b\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"b9 c-r-m-r-t-r\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"t\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"m\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u201cIf you like me\u201d game\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe sense of game is in meeting new interesting people. Many people know how hard it is to show attention to the women first and do not get any attention back. With the game on our site you will be able to check if the feeling is mutual and establish new contacts basing on the matches during the game.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"b\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<d