can write them short letter inviting to chat and probably after such invitation they will come there. Remember that not all the women percept it normal when some unknown man is inviting them to chat, so probably it would be better if you exchange several messages with the woman until going to chat. \n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPhoto contests \u2013 one more possibility to meet a Russian woman\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWe have several photo contests for different categories of photos. Upload photos in your profile and put them for some photo contest. It is one more possibility to meet women besides mere rating. If some woman likes your photo and gives you 10 mark then you receive notification about it.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWhen you find a Russian woman with whom it is interesting to communicate do not wait for years until somebody will take decision for you. Be ready to take the next steps steps: go and meet her in her country or arrange meeting in some neutral country to see her in person. \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAfter you met the woman in person you may already know what you want from this woman \u2013 you can see if you are compatible with the woman, if you can have good relationships with her and if you want her to become your wife\u2026\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tOnline now! feature\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tOn our site you can see when the women have been on the site for the last time (online now!, visited within one hour, visited within one day etc). We have more than 100 000 Russian women registered on our site, everyday more than 10 000 women come online. On the first 100 pages in search result you can see the women who come to the site regularly and either are online now or visited it within one day. You can write a letter to such women and you can be sure to receive an answer soon.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u201cWaiting to hear from you\u201d\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAs it was already mentioned on our site for serious aquaintances with Russian women you can see when the woman was on the site for the last time in the ir profiles. If you see \u201cWaiting to hear from you\u201d inscription on profile of the woman it means that this woman did not visit her profile for some time (more than a week). You can send her a letter, she will receive notification about it to her personal email and probably after that she will come to the site again.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u201cI have not been contacted for some time\u201d\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThere are many nice looking and interesting women on our personals site who for some reason did not receive a real letter for some time (only winks, postcards, etc) for more than 3 days. In that case the system automatically recalculates it and sets profiles of such women in a separate gallery \"I have not been contacted for